            <h3>This Blog</h3>
            <p>On this blog, I share tutorials, project walkthroughs, and thoughts about the latest trends in technology. I believe in learning by doing and hope that my content helps others on their coding journey.</p>
            
            <h3>Beyond Coding</h3>
